&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Account Executive - Dallas&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why We Have This Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;Our Account Executive team is composed of highly driven, curious individuals dedicated to closing experience gaps for leading brands. Using the Qualtrics Experience Management SaaS platform, you’ll build deep, strategic relationships while hunting for new opportunities. You’ll thrive by digging beneath surface answers to understand client needs at their core, continuously learning, and collaborating cross-functionally to deliver transformative results.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How You’ll Find Success&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exhibits strong curiosity and coachability, eager to learn new skills and deepen knowledge through active questioning and collaboration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrates grit, work ethic, and motor to proactively pursue goals and drive impact.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effectively balances relationship-building with an ability to hunt and discover new business within a large book of accounts, currently managing 30-35 clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Business acumen with capability to understand client structures and dynamics, acting as a culture and team builder.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong communicator who influences and builds trust across stakeholders at multiple levels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How You’ll Grow&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clear, structured promotion path via Qualtrics’ auto-promotion framework and continuous Career Action Planning with your manager.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Access to internal mobility platform Qmobility for additional growth opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skill development in business acumen, complex negotiation, and consultative selling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Opportunity to expand expertise within strategic accounts and deepen client partnerships through travel and in-person engagement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Things You’ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage a broad book of business, with a focus on new business hunting (100% outbound).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with internal teams—including Professional Services, Implementation, and Subject Matter Experts—to align solutions with client needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay current on solution offerings and the competitive landscape to craft effective proposals and pricing strategies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execute a systematic approach to contract negotiations and multi-account management ensuring win-win outcomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage your curiosity and coachability to continuously improve performance and contribute to team success.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
