&lt;li class=&quot;li3&quot;&gt;Takes initiative and works entrepreneurially to achieve outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li3&quot;&gt;Strong track record of exceeding sales quotas consistently&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li3&quot;&gt;Skilled at acquiring and developing new clients within complex sales cycles&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li3&quot;&gt;Expert negotiator comfortable closing deals and managing contracts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li3&quot;&gt;Ability to sell complex SaaS platforms (specifically Qualtrics XM) to strategic accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li3&quot;&gt;Clear and compelling communicator with storytelling skills to connect features to client needs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li3&quot;&gt;Comfortable working in a bilingual environment with strong proficiency in Chinese and English&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
